What's new in this release:

• AI-powered dish ingredients — Add to grocery list now generates dish-specific ingredients via Gemini AI, matched to your app language
• Gemini AI for meal planning, nutrition advice, and grocery lists — all AI features now use Gemini 2.0 Flash Lite when a free API key is configured
• Add your free Gemini API key in Account settings — clear setup UI with a direct link to Google AI Studio
• Plan tab shows a prompt when no key is configured so you know exactly what to do
• 2-step registration — sign up now captures your display name and household name upfront
• Auth screen polish: centred branding footer with designer credit
• Stability improvements: fixed stuck loading spinners and cancellation handling in AI flows
